{"tid":947146,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"軍費增至近2萬億抗中朝俄 日購逾百F-35　護衞艦變「航母」","createTime":"2018-12-19T05:00:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-19T05:59:14.000Z","uid":25558,"like":10,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"3cce06f497bcb7b95d4f96146e823a7353bd80f8","tid":947146,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:00:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181219/20571855\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181219%2F20571855&d=jwGvS68r2ymNx0b%2BIwoJjU4boqMkoHyMuoHHSR1H%2BGk%3D&h=fb3ee062\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Fdaily%2Farticle%2F20181219%2F20571855&h=58803fca\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/daily/article/20181219/20571855</a><br />\n<br />\n2018年12月19日 <br />\n<br />\n軍費增至近2萬億抗中朝俄<br />\n日購逾百F-35　護衞艦變「航母」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181219/large/19wj101p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181219%2Flarge%2F19wj101p.jpg&h=0f009f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n「出雲號」未來將改裝成具「航母」級別的多用途護衞艦。美聯社<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n日本內閣昨日通過新《防衞計劃大綱》及《中期防衞力整備計劃》，除了未來五年軍費將增加至歷史新高水平的24.47萬億日圓（1.91萬億港元），最矚目是將會把兩艘「出雲級」直升機護衞艦，改裝成達航母級別的「多用途護衞艦」，是二戰後首次，對抗中國、俄羅斯和北韓的軍事挑戰。<br />\n<br />\n大綱指出美國仍是世界上最強大的國家，但中國正在日本附近水域出動更多艦隻及戰機，而俄羅斯的空軍力量繼續威脅日本並在北方四島增建軍營，加上北韓尚未就摧毀其核彈力量兌現任何承諾，這些考慮目前最影響着日本的國防思維。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n相關新聞：俄北方四島擴建軍營<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/apple-photos/apple/20181219/large/19wj102p.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fapple-photos%2Fapple%2F20181219%2Flarge%2F19wj102p.jpg&h=368da341&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nF-35戰機<br />\n<br />\n可垂直升降<br />\n<br />\n目前日本擁有兩艘「出雲級」直升機護衞艦，「出雲號」及「加賀號」均是海上自衞隊最大型軍艦，其中「出雲號」會率先改裝。改裝後兩艦均能搭載10架可垂直升降的F-35B，排水量亦達二戰時日本擁有的航空母艦級別。防衞省官員強調護衞艦只在有國防需要的時候用作「航空母艦」。日本海上自衞隊所有艦隻均劃為護衞艦。<br />\n<br />\n另外，日本將向美國購買105架F-35隱形戰機，其中可在「出雲級」護衞艦升降的F-35B型戰機將佔42架、A型則佔63架；加上早前已訂購的42架F-35戰機，日本10年後將擁有147架F-35戰機。<br />\n<br />\n其他將採購的軍備，包括防空雷達、預警機等。日本早前在特朗普施壓下，向美國承諾增購軍備，減少美國的貿易逆差及規避貿易戰風險。<br />\n<br />\n日本除着眼於海陸空，更要在太空、網絡空間等「新領域」構建「多元綜合防衞力」，因此提出建立「太空專門部隊」、「通過擴充網絡防衞隊以保持網絡反擊能力」。<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n稱合乎憲法<br />\n<br />\n內閣官房長官菅義偉解釋，軍費上升是「在安全環境急速變化下，保持真正有效的防衞力」。至於改裝「出雲級」護衞艦惹來有違反和平憲法中不得擁有攻擊型航母之嫌，菅義偉認為合乎憲法；防衞大臣岩屋毅亦表示改裝直升機護衞艦未違自衞隊「專守防衞」原則。<br />\n<br />\n中國外交部發言人華春瑩昨日回應時稱，日本文件「老調重彈」，煽動所謂中國威脅，又指日本這種做法不利於中日關係改善發展，也不利於地區和平穩定大局，中方對此表示強烈不滿和反對，已向日方提出嚴正交涉，敦促日方堅持「專守防衞」的政策承諾。<br />\n<br />\n共同社/法新社/美聯社  <br />\n<br />\n下一則<br />\n下一則<br />\n俄北方四島擴建軍營"},{"pid":"c126ac7e85260226141ecd92d026a99f88957e7f","tid":947146,"uid":141151,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:06:40.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/support.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d08ae1130a5731b1369d52f14c1cc319c1f817c2","tid":947146,"uid":37384,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:08:30.000Z","msg":"趁你支那病<br />\n撚多你幾錢重<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/eating.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03d16bf7739d4a672d803831e119d329bedd94b3","tid":947146,"uid":85461,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:08:34.000Z","msg":"大日本帝國 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b03a0a75072f84cb8e33634883f4880ec3cecdcb","tid":947146,"uid":64009,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:09:09.000Z","msg":"十卜<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n支那有咩資格對他國事務指手劃腳"},{"pid":"6730bc04058f310f74fab46c2a0853e9a4aef2f6","tid":947146,"uid":79563,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:09:35.000Z","msg":"日本玩到咁癲, 都只係 0.9% GDP<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4c19542701ae7880058c7e965509d463a254d306","tid":947146,"uid":19501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"支那軍費多日本唔知幾多，仲好意思話人軍國主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1f52aaac631e0fc8d044fd3d6c7f6ac9c7a57c3e","tid":947146,"uid":79563,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"quote":{"pid":"4c19542701ae7880058c7e965509d463a254d306","tid":947146,"uid":19501,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:13:15.000Z","msg":"支那軍費多日本唔知幾多，仲好意思話人軍國主義<img src=\"/assets/faces/dogxm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:21:38.000Z","msg":"究竟邊個係軍國主義?<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lihkg.com/540/https://i.postimg.cc/Xqzyh2jL/image.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi.lihkg.com%2F540%2Fhttps%3A%2F%2Fi.postimg.cc%2FXqzyh2jL%2Fimage.jpg&h=a15ffa81&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"db785f5a55932da4c1a8236d9039651e3c95f6a5","tid":947146,"uid":79563,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-19T05:22:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2018/02/thediplomat-ap_630030771881-386x246.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2018%2F02%2Fthediplomat-ap_630030771881-386x246.jpg&h=7b5c82ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://thediplomat.com/wp-content/uploads/2016/12/thediplomat_2016-12-01_17-41-30-386x276.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fthediplomat.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F2016%2F12%2Fthediplomat_2016-12-01_17-41-30-386x276.jpg&h=0d